{   
    "speakers": {
        "npc": {
          "name": "Battle Tower Clerk",
          "face": {
            "type": "artificial",
            "modelType": "npc",
            "identifier": "cobblemon:shopman",
            "isLeftSide": true
          }
        }
      },
    "pages": [
        {
            "id": "greeting",
            "speaker": "npc",
            "lines": [
                "¡Bienvenido a la Torre Batalla!"
            ],
            "input": {
                "type": "option",
                "vertical": false,
                "options": [
                    {
                        "text": "Next",
                        "value": "next",
                        "action": "q.dialogue.set_page('page2');"
                    }
                ]
            }
        },
        {
            "id": "page2",
            "speaker": "npc",
            "lines": [
                "¿Te gustaría aceptar el desafío de la Sala de Batalla?"
            ],
            "input": {
                "type": "option",
                "vertical": false,
                "options": [
                    {
                        "text": "Yes",
                        "value": "yes",
                        "action": "q.dialogue.set_page('page3');"
                    },
                    {
                        "text": "Info",
                        "value": "info",
                        "action": "q.dialogue.set_page('info1');"
                    },
                    {
                        "text": "No",
                        "value": "no",
                        "action": "q.dialogue.set_page('end');"
                    }
                ]
            }
        },
        {
            "id": "page3",
            "speaker": "npc",
            "lines": [
                "Ahora te llevaré a la Sala de Batalla."
            ],
            "input": {
                "type": "option",
                "vertical": false,
                "options": [
                    {
                        "text": "Close",
                        "value": "close",
                        "action": [
                            "q.run_command('execute as ' + q.player.username + ' run scoreboard players set @s TriggerCommand 2');",
                            "q.dialogue.close();"
                            ]
                    }
                ]
            }
        },

        {
            "id": "info1",
            "speaker": "npc",
            "lines": [
                "La Torre Batalla es una instalación para desafíos de Batalla."
            ],
            "input": {
                "type": "option",
                "vertical": false,
                "options": [
                    {
                        "text": "Next",
                        "value": "next",
                        "action": "q.dialogue.set_page('info2');"
                    }
                ]
            }
        },
        {
            "id": "info2",
            "speaker": "npc",
            "lines": [
                "Una vez dentro, tu desafío dura hasta que pierdas."
            ],
            "input": {
                "type": "option",
                "vertical": false,
                "options": [
                    {
                        "text": "Next",
                        "value": "next",
                        "action": "q.dialogue.set_page('info3');"
                    }
                ]
            }
        },
        {
            "id": "info3",
            "speaker": "npc",
            "lines": [
                "En nuestro formato de Combate Individual, entras con solo tres Pokémon. Si llevas más, no podrás desafiar."
            ],
            "input": {
                "type": "option",
                "vertical": false,
                "options": [
                    {
                        "text": "Next",
                        "value": "next",
                        "action": "q.dialogue.set_page('info4');"
                    }
                ]
            }
        },
        {
            "id": "info4",
            "speaker": "npc",
            "lines": [
                "Los Pokémon de cada uno de nuestros entrenadores se ajustarán al nivel de tu Pokémon de mayor nivel."
            ],
            "input": {
                "type": "option",
                "vertical": false,
                "options": [
                    {
                        "text": "Next",
                        "value": "next",
                        "action": "q.dialogue.set_page('info5');"
                    }
                ]
            }
        },
        {
            "id": "info5",
            "speaker": "npc",
            "lines": [
                "Hay una cantidad ilimitada de entrenadores, ¡puedes luchar tanto como quieras o puedas!"
            ],
            "input": {
                "type": "option",
                "vertical": false,
                "options": [
                    {
                        "text": "Next",
                        "value": "next",
                        "action": "q.dialogue.set_page('info6');"
                    }
                ]
            }
        },
        {
            "id": "info6",
            "speaker": "npc",
            "lines": [
                "Si logras derrotar a tu oponente, ganarás Puntos de Batalla (BP)."
            ],
            "input": {
                "type": "option",
                "vertical": false,
                "options": [
                    {
                        "text": "Next",
                        "value": "next",
                        "action": "q.dialogue.set_page('info7');"
                    }
                ]
            }
        },
        {
            "id": "info7",
            "speaker": "npc",
            "lines": [
                "A medida que crezca tu Racha de Batalla, los entrenadores también se volverán más difíciles con Pokémon más difíciles."
            ],
            "input": {
                "type": "option",
                "vertical": false,
                "options": [
                    {
                        "text": "Next",
                        "value": "next",
                        "action": "q.dialogue.set_page('info8');"
                    }
                ]
            }
        },
        {
            "id": "info8",
            "speaker": "npc",
            "lines": [
                "Salir de la Torre tras una victoria no afectará tu Racha de Batalla, solo perder contra los entrenadores de la torre."
            ],
            "input": {
                "type": "option",
                "vertical": false,
                "options": [
                    {
                        "text": "Next",
                        "value": "next",
                        "action": "q.dialogue.set_page('info9');"
                    }
                ]
            }
        },
        {
            "id": "info9",
            "speaker": "npc",
            "lines": [
                "Si quieres interrumpir o pausar tu desafío, ¡acude a la Enfermera Joy para salir!"
            ],
            "input": {
                "type": "option",
                "vertical": false,
                "options": [
                    {
                        "text": "Next",
                        "value": "next",
                        "action": "q.dialogue.set_page('page2');"
                    }
                ]
            }
        },



        {
            "id": "end",
            "speaker": "npc",
            "lines": [
                "Esperamos verte de nuevo."
            ],
            "input": {
                "type": "option",
                "vertical": false,
                "options": [
                    {
                        "text": "Close",
                        "value": "close",
                        "action": [
                            "q.dialogue.close();"
                            ]
                    }
                ]
            }
        }
        ]
    }